    Notes on tags used in MITgcmUV
    ==============================

o tapenade & genmake2:
  - in genmake2, import Tapenade command arguments from ad-optfile (adjoint_tap)
  - allow additional extra arguments with TAP_EXTRA, which can also be set using
    new command line option "-tap_extra" ;
  - add support for Tapenade to skip checkpointing with new "_FWD" and "_BWD"
    versions of manually written subroutine derivatives ;
  - test new "no-checkpointing" feature in halfpipe_streamice experiment
    with new reference output.
o pkg/gmredi:
  - remove OLD_VISBECK_CALC code ; rename S/R GMREDI_CALC_PSI_B ;
  - unless restricted to only uniform Kappa (including 2-D & 1-D scaling),
    define local 3-d vars for Kappa-Redi and Kappa-GM to simplify Tensor
    setting and Psi-Bolus code.

