    if rAc is uniform) by using few more domain global quantities (in GRID.h).
  - adjust accordingly cg2g/cg3d TargetResWunit in all forward test exp. to keep
    identical results but switch off cg2dTargetResWunit in most AD exp. (except
    if using useNSACGSolver=T) to use cg2gTargetResidual (normalize cg2d RHS).
