checkpoint69f (2025/07/10)
o model/src, pkg/kpp:
  - store shortwave penetration fraction in 3D field SWFrac3D and add run-time
    params "selectPenetratingSW" to chose between different short-wave heating
    options (only =1 currently implemented);
  - remove local (buggy) solution in pkg/seaice ;
  - add runtime-flag "KPPuseSWfrac3D", set to F by default, because this code
    can only approximately replace the original pkg/kpp-code ;
  - update TAF directives in pkg/kpp (mostly related to the code changes);
  - fix "global_ocean.cs32x15" exp bug in "in_p" and "seaice" tests, update FWD,
    ADM & TLM ref. output ; set KPPuseSWfrac3D to True in "1D_ocean_ice_column"
    (both FWD & ADM) test exp. with updated ref. output.
o pkg/streamice:
  - fix "new_partial" initialisation in streamice_adv_front.f (helps Tapenade)
o pkg/bling, pkg/dic:
  - additional store directives to avoid hidden recomputations.
o pkg/longstep:
  - add remaining GM-Redi matrix coefficients (extra-diagonal & diagonal terms)
    and Bolus transport stream function for time-averaging in longstep pkg and
    use saved values in longstep time-stepping.
o pkg/seaice:
  - fix 3 output formats to allow to run with gfortran v.15
  - also add "deep_anelastic.vecinv" to multi-threaded tests.
o pkg/mom_{common,fluxform,vecinv}:
  - mom_fluxform, new option, selectCoriScheme=4: use hFac averaged transport in
    Coriolis term so that column integral of tendency match Coriolis time
    column integral U,V.
  - mom_vecinv, new option, selectVortScheme=4: by-pass division by hFacZ and
    instead apply recip_hFacW/S on final tendency. Note: this fixes Angular-Mom
    (AM) conservation but breaks vorticity tendency matching advection of vort.
  - new 3-d Coriolis option, select3dCoriScheme=2,3: Alternative discretization
    using averaged transport; =3 (vs 2), an other alternative discretization of
    vertical momentum tendency gW.
  - deep-model, put gU,gV NH-metric terms inside vertical advection, to exactly
    conserves AM (+ simplify & speed up by skipping NH metric-terms gU,gV
    calculation). Add CPP option "MOM_USE_OLD_DEEP_VERT_ADV" (in
    MOM_COMMON_OPTIONS.h) to recover the explicit NH metric-term calculation.
  - mom_fluxform, new spherical Metric-terms option, selectMetricTerms=2,3: More
    accurate discretization similar to manual eq. 2.102 & 2.103 but centered at
    grid-cell corner; Also option (selectMetricTerms=3) to skip the gU spherical
    metric term by advecting uVel*dxC (simpler, faster and exactly conserve AM).
  - add diagnostics for Metric-Terms.
  - verification exp. "deep_anelastic", new secondary "vecinv" test + also
    update primary test ref output.

