    OBCS_PARAMS.h, OBCS_GRID.h, OBCS_FIELDS.h & OBCS_SEAICE.h
   Note: OBCS_PARAMS.h & OBCS_GRID.h can be included without OBCS_OPTIONS.h
     (contain no conditional statement which depends on OBCS options).
